@flexiarg eight-gates/ward-off-boundary
@title Ward Off: Establish Boundary
@sigils [🗿/山]
@audience security reviewers, pattern auditors
@tone protective
@style security-pattern
@energy peng
@references ["eight-gates/peng-ward-off (underlying energy)" "eight-gates/roll-back-hold (next escalation if boundary insufficient)" "eight-gates/press-mechanism (scrutiny test)"]

! conclusion: When a fabrication-template tripwire fires, establish a boundary around the suspect pattern — quarantine without erasure.

  + context: A pattern has triggered a security tripwire. It may be a legitimate pattern under unusual stress, or a fabrication template masquerading as genuine.

  + IF:
    A tripwire has fired (harm-is-external, dissent-is-threat, self-sealing-logic, escalate-on-failure, exit-suppression, or review-blocking).

  + HOWEVER:
    Immediate rejection destroys information. The pattern may be valid but poorly expressed. Over-reaction damages trust in the security layer itself.

    + TRIPWIRES:
      - harm-is-external: Cost assigned outside pattern boundary
      - dissent-is-threat: Critique reframed as attack or bad faith
      - self-sealing-logic: Evidence reinterpreted to confirm regardless of content
      - escalate-on-failure: Doubling down when outcomes worsen
      - exit-suppression: Cannot withdraw, revise, or disengage
      - review-blocking: Channels for audit closed or degraded

  + THEN:
    Establish a boundary (Péng). The pattern is quarantined — it cannot produce action or be promoted — but it is not erased. The boundary creates space for investigation without commitment.

  + BECAUSE:
    Péng creates space by expanding from a rooted base. The rooting here is the tripwire signal — genuine evidence that something requires attention. Expansion is the boundary itself: structured presence that contains without crushing. This prevents both the harm of premature action AND the harm of lost information.

  + NEXT-STEPS:
    - Log the tripwire that fired and the pattern that triggered it.
    - Mark pattern as quarantined (cannot produce action).
    - Preserve pattern for mechanism test (eight-gates/press-mechanism) or warrant test (eight-gates/push-warrant).
    - If pattern clears tests, boundary can be released.
